    Contains the expected time it takes to travel along the specified path, which is for one stop to another. There can be a different list of TravelTimesForStopPath for each trip. The idea is to share travel times when possible, when they are relatively the same for a trip pattern. But if a trip needs separate travel times then it can have it.
